(1, '', '1801', 'Profile', '<p><big><strong>Company Name:</strong> Doctors In Service Limited (DIS)</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>Company Address:</strong> AD 860 Abura, Cape Coast, Central Region, Ghana</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>Phone:</strong> +233 244 850 865/+233 579 290 027</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>Telephone:</strong> +233 332 138 585</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>Company Email:</strong>&nbsp;info@doctorsinservice.com</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>Company Website:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.doctorsinservice.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.doctorsinservice.com</a></big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>Branches:</strong>&nbsp;Cape Coast, Takoradi and Kasoa</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p><big><strong>Primary Line of Business</strong>: Health Care Delivery</big></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>OUR WORKFORCE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our currently workforce is nearly 60, with some being doctors, nurses, gynecologist, administrators, pharmacists, optometrists, accountants, finance manager, operations manager and other supporting staffs. This number is expected to increase by the end of the year and the coming years due to the establishment of new branches and other projects.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>KEY PROCESSES</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We operate with the state of the art health facility and also with a well-qualified professional doctors and nurses who render quality health care. Some of the services are stated below.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our Strength</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We have a strong brand in the Central Region of Ghana and our brand is synonymous with quality healthcare.</li>\r\n	<li>We have a strong market share among the middle class and elite.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'IMG_20171122_105502.jpg', ''),
(2, '', '9976', 'History', '<h2><kbd><var><big><strong>HISTORY OF DOCTORS IN SERVICE </strong></big></var></kbd></h2>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>In March 2011, <strong><em>Dr. Andrew Herzuah</em></strong>, a medical doctor, then a house officer started serving people in their homes at the request of relatives who considered he could do such. His love for work sometimes saw him not charging anything for such work. This also sometimes was fueled by his passion to see patients comfortable irrespective of whether he is paid or not. It was during one of such home care services that he landed a strategic property which later became the first home of Doctors in Service Limited. The company initially was to focus on home care services and discussions on those were held with a few people. However, the plan of God was different. We were to move into ambulatory clinics whose mission was to provide a fast, affordable client centered and quality healthcare for the numerous middle and upper class who often are frustrated by the slow, painful process of seeking medical attention in the public system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It started with staff strength of 8 persons and locum doctors with a lot of hard work, training and retraining of staff on excellent customer care, quality service and so on. The company stuck to three main principles:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Providing fast but&nbsp;quality services</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Providing a friendly and nice environment for patient care</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Putting the patients&rsquo; needs first in all we do</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>We focused on aggressive awareness creation in the first 6 months by focusing on different strategies. This saw our patient to out rise steadily from an average of 5 patients per day to 30 patients per day by the end of the first year.<br />\r\nThere has been steady growth in staff, patient tout, revenue, logistics, equipment&rsquo;s and skilled human resource.<br />\r\nCurrently seeing averagely 40 patients per day after 18 months in operation and being <em>one of the preferred healthcare</em> destinations among the middle and upper class, the company is strategically positioned for continuous growth, better services and expansion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'history.jpg', ''),
(3, '', '3613', 'Vision', '<p><strong>Our vision</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lsquo;&rsquo;To be the ultimate brand in total healthcare service provision and healthcare innovation in Africa&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Our mission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&lsquo;&rsquo;To provide a quality, affordable, efficient and convenient total healthcare service which is principally hinged on utmost client satisfaction and continually bring out innovative services which meet our clients&rsquo; changing needs&rsquo;&rsquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 'vision.jpg', ''),
(4, '', '6697', 'Core Values', '<p>The company is founded on <em><strong>four basic core values</strong></em>;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Compassion</li>\r\n	<li>Efficiency and promptness</li>\r\n	<li>Integrity and honesty</li>\r\n	<li>High sense of quality</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', '', ''),
